'''Sidi Bouhlel''' ([[Wikipedia:Arabic language|Arabic]]: سيدى بحلال) is a [[Wikipedia:marabout|marabout]] in south west [[Tunisia]] near to the town [[Wikipedia:Tozeur|Tozeur]].

[[Jundland Wastes]] on [[Tatooine]] shots for [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''A New Hope'']] and [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']] were taken in a nearby canyon commonly known as the Star Wars canyon. It was also used for filming [[Wikipedia:Raiders of the Lost Ark|''Raiders of the Lost Ark'']] and [[Wikipedia:The English Patient (film)|''The English Patient'']].

